rental.headline: FAMILY HOME ON APPROX 800 SQM
rental.description:
Occupy an enviable, neat 4 bedroom size north facing residence offering you lot features with a cottage feeling in a quiet yet convenient location in one of the best street at the Parramatta council side of Toongabbie in an 800 sqm area. Max 2 min to a primary school, 5 min to a child care, 7- 10 min to Toongabbie station/ shops plus a fantastic neighbourhood a bonus. 3 good size bedrooms all with big built-in wardrobes plus a family retreat room. -Separate Spacious Lounge, separate dining area, separate Kitchen and separate laundry area. -Modern Kitchen with Gas cooking, Dishwasher and plenty of storage -Generous floor area showcase stunning Timber flooring with amble sky lights to fill the natural light thorough out the house and nice floor level new curtains. -Internal laundry with costly front loading washing machine and double draw dishwasher. -Separate bath/shower and toilet. -35 SQM Deck covered with Pergola at the back overlooking 500 sqm well maintained backyard with costly fruit plants, herbs and ornamental plants. -At least 3 car spaces within the property besides the off street parking. -Air conditioning and security alarm.
Don't hesitate or it will be gone. Please ring your Exclusive agents Atul Bhanushali on 0402961515 or Tanmay Goswami on 0447270063
